'''千屈菜科'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Lythraceae}}）， 包括32[[属|属]]大约500-600[[种|种]][[植物|植物]]，绝大部分是[[草本|草本]]，也有少数[[灌木|灌木]]或[[乔木|乔木]]。广泛分布在全世界[[热带|热带]]和[[温带|温带]]地区。

2003年的[[APG_II_分类法|APG II 分类法]]将[[石榴科|石榴科]]和菱科劃歸成為千屈菜科的亞科。

== 分配 ==
千屈菜科廣泛分佈，但大多數物種熱帶和一些溫帶。<ref name="Stevens 20012">{{cite web|title=Angiosperm Phylogeny Website|url=http://www.mobot.org/mobot/research/apweb/|access-date=15 February 2011|author=Stevens, P.F.|date=2001{{ndash}}2011|archive-date=2016-05-15|archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160515135116/http://www.mobot.org/MOBOT/research/APweb/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Judd 2008">{{cite book|last=Judd|first=Walter S.|author2=Christopher S. Campbell|author3=Elizabeth A. Kellogg|author3link=Elizabeth Anne Kellogg|author4=Peter F. Stevens|author4-link=Peter F. Stevens|author5=Michael J. Donoghue|title=Plant Systematics: A Phylogenetic Approach|url=https://archive.org/details/plantsystematics0000unse|edition=3rd|year=2008|publisher=Sinauer Associates|location=Sunderland, MA|isbn=978-0-87893-407-2|pages=[https://archive.org/details/plantsystematics0000unse/page/412 412]–414}}</ref> 他們在撒哈拉沙漠和澳大利亞最乾旱的地區不存在。<ref name="Stevens 20012" /> 許多物種出現在水生或半水生棲息地（Decodon、Didiplis、Rotala、Sonneratia、Trapa）。<ref name="Judd 2008" /><ref name="Mabberley 20083">{{cite book|author-link=David Mabberley|last=Mabberley|first=David J.|title=Mabberley's Plant Book: A portable dictionary of plants, their classification and uses|url=https://archive.org/details/mabberleysplantb00mabb|edition=3rd|year=2008|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge|isbn=978-0-521-82071-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/mabberleysplantb00mabb/page/n505 508]}}</ref>

